headline: Wonderinterest Assessed Investments in Top Sustainable Global Companies
summary: Wonderinterest Trading, a regulated investment firm operating across global markets, assessed sustainability-focused investing by analyzing the leading companies as presented in the Dow Jones Sustainability World Index (DJSI World).
